// SYNTAX TEST "Packages/ct_todo/todo.sublime-syntax"
todo
----
* sublime syntax
- expand block (##)
- folding
- auto new list item
- move finished _groups_ to bottom
+ account for -word (missing space)
+ new format style (see block below)
+ add to readme (become, *)
+ expand page headings (==)
+ expand section headings (--)
+ handle unsaved files
+ remove prioritsed lists (1)
+ text blocks

shortcuts
- mark as hp todo: ctrl + alt + 8
- mark as todo: ctrl + alt + -
- mark as lp todo: ctrl + alt + shift + 8
- mark as doing: ctrl + alt + .
- mark as done: ctrl + alt + =
- mark as unsure: ctrl + alt + /
- mark as separate list: ctrl + alt + \
- mark as delegated: ctrl + alt + shift + \

commands
--------
- clear done
- mark as [todo, doing, question, done]
- run formatter
- merge into one (heading: item)
- split into many
- move [group, page] [up, down]
- promote / demote

